    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Morphological and molecular taxonomic analysis of Pseudopoda Jäger, 2000 (Araneae: Sparassidae: Heteropodinae) in Sichuan Province, China" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239528>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239529>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239530> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239528>
    dc:description "FIGURES 115 – 123. Pseudopoda wu spec. nov., holotype male (115 – 119) and female paratype (120 – 123: PJ 3491) from Lugu Lake. 115 – 118 Male left palp (115 prolateral, 116 ventral, 117 retrolateral, 118 dorsal); 119 Embolus tip, ventral. 120 epigyne, ventral. 121, 123 Vulva (121 dorsal, 123 frontal). 122 Schematic course of internal duct system, dorsal. C—conductor." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239528/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239529>
    dc:description "FIGURES 124 – 129. Pseudopoda wu spec. nov., male (124 – 126) and female paratype (127 – 129: PJ 3491) from Lugu Lake, habitus (124, 127 dorsal, 125, 128 ventral, 126, 129 frontal)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239529/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239530>
    dc:description "FIGURE 130. Map of Sichuan with records of Pseudopoda spp. (Pseudopoda sp. cf. yunnanensis not mapped). Pseudopoda grahami (Fox, 1936) and P. exigua (Fox, 1938) are included as described from Sichuan although no new records are known and therefore not mentioned in the text." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239530/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

